Source.Name: phoronix-test-suite
Source.Description: The Phoronix Test Suite is a comprehensive testing and benchmarking platform. It allows for carrying out tests in a fully automated manner from test installation to execution and reporting. All tests are meant to be easily reproducible, easy-to-use, and support fully automated execution.
